node.text:
We were fortunate enough to spend a weekend in Yokosuka, Japan entertaining the families living on the base there. We would like to thank the staff of the HMS Albion for their wonderful tour. 
Featuring Dakota Roche, Gary Young, Matthias Dandois, Josh Borden and Omar Hassan.

Video: Colin Mackay

node.text: @Leewdogg had a big weekend out with @FiendBMX and our man @JeffZPhoto tagged along to capture for us. Lewis showed up wearing the Dennis Enarson Off The Wall Classic Tee. You’ll have to wait a little to see the clips Lewis and Fiend are working on, but you know they’ll be fire!

node.text: Happy Birthday @TreyJonesucks! Trey joined us in 2011 and is still killing it today. Wait until you see his new video part he’s working on right now that will be out later in the year! Check out his latest work on @UnClickedPodcast to get to know Trey better and to hear him out on some big topics. Photo: @ColinMackayBMX @RADShare
